560
00:48:09,000 --> 00:48:10,040
You did this yourself?

561
00:48:11,520 --> 00:48:12,520
Yeah.

562
00:48:12,800 --> 00:48:13,800
I don't want it.

563
00:48:14,170 --> 00:48:15,170
Just take it.

564
00:48:16,170 --> 00:48:17,970
Don't turn down a gift, man.

565
00:48:19,590 --> 00:48:21,000
Use it as a rag if you want.

566
00:48:21,280 --> 00:48:22,760
We're parting ways, right?

567
00:48:23,660 --> 00:48:24,780
What do you mean?

568
00:48:25,200 --> 00:48:26,520
