579
00:49:05,280 --> 00:49:08,400
You told me things can't go back
to the way they were.

580
00:49:10,440 --> 00:49:11,440
Forget it.

581
00:49:23,920 --> 00:49:24,920
Okay.

582
00:49:26,800 --> 00:49:28,050
